# Optional cloud sync (Supabase). Copy this file to `.env.local` and fill in
# your project's values to enable accounts + cross-device sync. Leave unset and
# the app runs fully local/offline with no account.
#
# Find these in the Supabase dashboard: Project Settings → API.
# Both are PUBLIC (the publishable key is meant to ship in the client) — Row
# Level Security protects the data. Never put a secret (sb_secret_…) /
# service-role key here.
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=
VITE_SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=
